This two-building, 60,000 SF complex is located in Chesterland, Ohio. Situated in a semi-rural setting, 8834-8844 Mayfield Road is just minutes
from the Mayfield/SOM Center Road Interchange
of I-271, allowing for easy access to the Cleveland market. The combination of light industrial, Class A office, and 38 acres of land allow for a variety of potential uses including regional headquarters opportunities for users or investors.
